<!-- Node: "ModDb get's a face lift." -->
<div class="body_box_header">ModDb get's a face lift.</div>
<div class="body_box"><small>Submitted by <a href="http://www.gamedesign.net/user/view/2198" title="View user profile.">Andy</a> on Thursday, September 23, 2004 - 06:08</small><br /><br />
<!--submitted by Andy-->
<H4>Mod Database V2 Update</h4>
After a year of development the time has finally come to unleash<br> Mod Database v2.<br>
Whilst the new site will appear similar to the present one, it has undergone over 200 changes. <br>Each of these was implemented to carry this site onto bigger and better things.<br> Here are the notable updates:
<br /><br />
