<!-- Node: "DOOM 3 Demo released" -->
<div class="body_box_header">DOOM 3 Demo released</div>
<div class="body_box"><small>Submitted by <a href="http://www.gamedesign.net/user/view/2157" title="View user profile.">Method</a> on Sunday, September 19, 2004 - 16:11</small><br /><br />
<a href = "http://www.idsoftware.com/">id Software</a> released <a href = "http://www.fileplanet.com/files/140000/145822.shtml">DOOM 3 demo</a> (470 MB), it includes first 3 levels from the retail version. This should be enough to convince you to buy the game, if you haven't already.
